{"tid":592763,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子新清水灣道天橋墮橋亡","createTime":"2018-03-14T12:59:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-14T12:59:43.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bfeff734d7d4201ded957654aeafc2ac3b5cc276","tid":592763,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T12:59:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180314/large/1521030350_1bec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180314%2Flarge%2F1521030350_1bec.jpg&h=16227906&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一部客貨車駛至新清水灣道行人天橋下時，司機見有人倒卧馬路上，立即急停。(溫文學攝)<br />\n<br />\n曾多次發生墮橋事件的新清水灣道天橋再添亡魂，晚上7時許，一名老翁在新清水灣道行人天橋攀過鐵欄，一躍而下，直墮50米下的行車線，當場重創昏迷，剛巧一部客貨車駛至，司機見有人倒卧馬路上，立即急停，並報警求助。老翁事後由救護車送院搶救，惜證實不治。警方正調查其墮橋原因。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180314/57946898\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180314%2F57946898&d=8aBMm4NG%2BqopGMwwVxN5qBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=a71c58eb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180314%2F57946898&h=3f685324\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180314/57946898</a>"}]}